                    "name": "Dislodged Armor",
                    "ability_type": "automatic",
                    "text": "Once the coralclaw is reduced to half its Hit Points, its AC decreases by 2, it gains a +5 circumstance bonus to its Speeds, and it loses coral camouflage. A coralclaw can repair its coral armor with 4 hours of work."
